===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

#{{uncountable}} The act of [[hang]]ing a person (or oneself) by the neck in order to [[execute]] that person (or to commit suicide).
#{{countable}} A public event at which a person is [[hang]]ed.
#:''The hanging of the bandits was attended by the whole village.''
#{{countable}} Anything wide, high and rather thin that is [[hang|hung]] as a [[decorative]] element (such as curtains, gobelins, wallpaper or posters).
#{{uncountable}} The way in which hangings (decorations) are arranged.
#:''I dislike the cramped hanging in the gallery of 18th century painters.''

